+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                 |
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: tvmaze.content                                                                                           |
|               |   Filter: tvmaze.request_path = Utf8("/shows/169")                                                                   |
|               |     TableScan: tvmaze projection=[request_path, content], partial_filters=[tvmaze.request_path = Utf8("/shows/169")] |
| physical_plan | CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                          |
|               |   FilterExec: request_path@0 = /shows/169, projection=[content@1]                                                    |
|               |     RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                            |
|               |       CooperativeExec                                                                                                |
|               |         HttpExec: base_url=https://api.tvmaze.com/, format=json, partitions=[(path="/shows/169", query="", body="")] |
|               |                                                                                                                      |
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
